---
import Container from '@/components/Container.astro';
---

<section id="process" class="py-24 bg-surface" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:section">
  <Container>
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:header">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:label">Hoe het werkt</h2>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:title">
        Ons Framework
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:grid">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border reveal" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:step-1">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary/10 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:num-1">01</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:h3-1">Analyseren</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:p-1">
          We starten met een grondige analyse van je huidige situatie en doelen. Op basis daarvan ontwikkelen we een funnel en campagnestrategie.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border reveal reveal-delay-1" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:step-2">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary/10 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:num-2">02</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:h3-2">Actieplan</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:p-2">
          Op basis van de analyse maken we een op maat gemaakt actieplan. Dit bevat een helder stappenplan en de verwachte resultaten.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border reveal reveal-delay-2" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:step-3">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary/10 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:num-3">03</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:h3-3">Briefing</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:p-3">
          Na jouw goedkeuring van het actieplan gaan we aan de slag. We briefen jou en ons team, zodat iedereen precies weet wat er moet gebeuren.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border reveal" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:step-4">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary/10 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:num-4">04</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:h3-4">Uitvoering</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:p-4">
          We zetten de plannen om in daden en lanceren je nieuwe funnel en campagnes. Vanaf dag één beginnen we met het aantrekken van nieuwe leads.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5 -->
      <div class="bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border reveal reveal-delay-1" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:step-5">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary/10 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:num-5">05</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:h3-5">Optimaliseren</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:p-5">
          Na de lancering monitoren en optimaliseren we de resultaten continu. Zo zorgen we ervoor dat je campagnes steeds beter presteren.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 6 -->
      <div class="bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border reveal reveal-delay-2" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:step-6">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary/10 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:num-6">06</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:h3-6">Evalueren</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:p-6">
          We rapporteren de resultaten, sturen wekelijkse updates en evalueren regelmatig samen met jou. Op basis daarvan maken we aanpassingen.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center reveal" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:footer">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground font-bold rounded-md hover:bg-secondary-hover transition-all no-underline" data-ps="src/components/home/Process.astro:cta">
        Contact opnemen
      </a>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
